    • getPropertyFromStore

      public CPSProperty getPropertyFromStore(String propertyName) throws ConfigurationPropertyStoreException
      A method to create a CPSProperty within the namespace If the namesapce is hidden, a null property is returned otherwise a property is created. If the property already exists in the store, the property's value from the store will be loaded into the property as well If the property does not exist in the store, the property's value will be null
